name: Keysax
content:
Keysax was a human male who served as a lieutenant in the Galactic Empire. Following the Ferrix incident, an Imperial Military force was deployed under the command of Captain Vanis Tigo. After ISB Supervisor Lieutenant Dedra Meero gained control of the Morlana sector from Supervisor Blevin, Keysax helped chase down Bix Caleen, a person of interest to the Empire. Eventually, Keysax was in a briefing alongside Supervisor Meero, ISB Attendant Corv, and Captain Tigo.
Keysax will debut in the Andor web-TV series, and is portrayed by Nick Moss. He was identified in an image asset release on Getty Images by Walt Disney Studios.
